subtitle: Honourable $dorm3d, allow me to show you how a truly great Royal Maid cleans a vase.
Hold it with one hand and gently wipe up and down.
Not too forcefully, but not too gently...
It's a delicate item, so one must be careful not to drop it...
There! It's all clean now!
Eep!
I-I mustn't trouble you with such a... Hyah?!
Thank you, my sweet, honourable $dorm3d. That will do.
Honourable $dorm3d, could you help me for a...
$dorm3d?
Even you have a mischievous side, I see.
Why, I'm most honoured...!
My adored $dorm3d...
I've been waiting for you, my honourable $dorm3d. Please, come in.
Oh? Do you consider this enough?
You're always too kind, $dorm3d.
Still, the honour of being able to serve you in a more... intimate, private setting has me trembling with joy.
Not at all! I just did what was expected of me as a maid.
It is a Royal Maid's duty to keep every location frequented by her $dorm3d spotless.
Umm... Actually, I fully prepared myself in anticipation of your visit today, my honourable $dorm3d!
This way, please.
Please forgive your poor excuse of a maid for the simplicity of her welcome.
If only I had more time, I could've prepared something more grand. Something more fitting.
I have prepared delicious tea that's just the temperature, premium refreshments that both taste lovely and are healthy.
There is also a well-tidied bed, and lastly, me. Everything has been made perfect for you.
Should you have any requests, I shall do all I can to fulfill them.
Wait... You're asking me to provide THAT service, are you not?
Finally, this day has come! How long I've waited to be with you in...
...You just assumed that I must be tired after all that, and wanted me to take a break?
Oh, so that's what you meant... Umm...
Although I am a little disappointed, I will fulfill your request.
Now then, please take a seat next to me on the couch, my honourable $dorm3d.
$dorm3d, I didn't think you'd come here to bathe, too!
Aah... Is it getting too hot in here, or is it just because I'm seeing you in a state of undress?
Such unbecoming thoughts are coming to mind...
I need to clean over here... and over there, too...
Scrub... Scrub...
Stupid Sirius, spilling so much tea... Causing so much trouble for your poor, honourable Master...
Ooh...
Master? You're trying to console me...?
Th-thank you, my honourable Master!
Just a little more...
Phew... That should do it!
Honourable Master? It's about time to wake up...
To think I get to wake up right beside you...
Were you able to sleep well, Master?
How did you like the bed? And the pillow? I strive to improve!
What an embarrassment of a maid I am, flaling asleep before her master did...
Oh, I-I'm so sorry... I didn't mean to...
Please, punish me for my insolence, my honourable Master!
Gueeess who?
Hmm... On second thought, I'm not suited for this little tease Sakawa taught me...
You thought it was cute? Oh, okay...
Alright, that should do it.
Aren't we leaving yet?
$dorm3d, lend me your hand.
Do you feel how hard my heart is beating?
It gets like this when... I'm with you...
You know, you don't get a foot massage like this every day.
This will improve my feet's circulation? Okay...
Mmh...
Feels warm... It's very nice.
Help me... Teacher!
Hmm... Teach...er...?
Hehe... Do you wanna play with Anchorage?
Together...!
Tap
Tap
Teacher... Anchorage is here!
Give me a hug...!
Teacher... Your hands are warm!
Teacher! W-wake up!
Kissing... learned!
Anchorage loves you!
Do you love Anchorage, Teacher...?
Teacher...! Paint... Anchorage will make art!
Hum hum~
Me... and Teacher! And... a heart!
Teacher! My paints fell...
It's okay...? Okay! Anchorage will... keep drawing!
Hmm... Umm...
Picture... Anchorage and Teacher, together forever...! Yeah!
Mmh…
Anchorage is... sorting through these!
It's tricky... but I'll try to do it myself!
A leaf? Stuck to me?
Where...? I can't see it!
Teacher... help Anchorage!
Thank you! I'm so happy!
Hmm... Hmmmm…
Huh? Oh, honey, you scared me! Are you curious about them?
Heheh, then you should try them on too!
Wow! They actually suit you super well!
That's my honey! You're too charming!
Hum dee dum♪ ...Ah!
Honey!
Haha, this way, silly!
You're cute even when you're all sad! Do you feel bad because you couldn't find me?
Don't worry! I'm always by your side, honey!
Phew... So relaxing! Strawberry flavor is the best♪
Oh, honey!
You gotta guess, honey. Here's a hint: It's sweet!
No cheating, now.
Okay, okay. You can have some, too!
Grr, you sneaky candy!
Huh? Is it reflecting light onto my chest?
Were you staring, honey? That's not good~
Ah! You wanted my candy, after all!
Nuh-uh! You promised I'd get to try it first!
Ooh! Honey, hurry up and feed it to me!
Mmm... I love the flavor you picked out!
Mmm... Thanks to your help, I feel better now. You deserve a reward!
Should I be a little more... forward right now, maybe?
Okay... Let's taste this sweet crystal candy together... *munch*
Tell me... Can you taste the fizzy green apple on my lips? Mwah…
Mm... Be a little gentler…
I might hit my head again.
Ouch... That hurts!
Honey, that tickles... Ambushes are no fair!
Nobody! Will disturb! My time with $dorm3d! May this door never open again... Heehee...
Hehe, $dorm3d~ The lock seems to have broken. I'm doing my best to repair it.
But let it be known that we are safe – and more importantly, alone!
You'll never leave my sight again♥
I have one of those, too.
$dorm3d, you will only look at Taihou... She will deal with all those pests...
Hmm? Mm... Look only at Taihou... You belong to Taihou... Zzz...
Umm...
Ah, $dorm3d...
I really, really want to keep that cup you used. Because...
No... As long as you're here, I suppose there is no need for "indirect" kisses.
Huh? Aaaaaah!
Urgh, now I've done it... $dorm3d! Help me, please!
$dorm3d! Save meeee!
$dorm3d... Hehe... There you have it. Are you surprised?
Aaahn! $dorm3d, is this what you're into?
If it is... come even closer for me~
The thing is... I accidentally cuffed my hands, and I can't escape.
Want to see them, $dorm3d?
But first... We'd better find that key!
Oh, my... Goodness, Commander...♡
$dorm3d~ Don't tell me...
Heehee, have I just discovered one of your... proclivities?
I'm ready any time~
I can't help but think you want it too, heehee♡
I can't believe it was right under my butt!
Can you tell, $dorm3d?
The thing I really want to lock up... is you!
Mm... Hmm? Just a little longer...
You came all this way, and that's all you're going to do?
A blanket? Come on...
Don't you think it's plenty warm enough already?
If you're still worried about me, then I say...
Ugh... Who decided to put this in such a hard-to-reach place?!
Gah?! How long have you been there?
Hey... Give me that. Right now!
Hyah?!
$dorm3d？！Are you okay?!$dorm3d？！
Perfect timing. Brush my hair for me, would you?
Be gentle, now. If you fail to satisfy me...
You'll be punished.
But if you do manage to please me...
Well, a handsome reward might be waiting for you.
I'm waiting, Commander.
Mmm!
Commander? Such fine wine begs to be savored, you know.
Drunk? Me? Heehee... What about you?
This wine is at its best when you're a little tipsy.
If you're not there yet, let me help you. Mmch...
How was that? Did I help make it a little more fun for you?
Now, give me your hand...
Your face... Isn't it getting just as hot as mine?
Hmm? You think it's just my imagination? I dunno... You look awfully red to me.
Was that our last glass? I guess I'll have to open another bottle...
It's a very fine vintage... I think you'll love the flavor.
Surely you're feeling the buzz now, Commander.
What? A little?
Goodness... You really know how to stimulate my competitive nature.
Doesn't the aroma of wine just make you swoon?
Do you smell it? That rich, full-flavored aroma?
Imagine how it must taste.
Come on. It's your turn to pour.
First, hold it firmly...
Oh. I didn't think you'd actually do it.
Nnh... I'm feeling a little dizzy...
I-I can't believe you... You certainly picked a time to be bold.
I-I expect you to take responsibility and clean up for me.
Heehee, that ought to get you good and drunk...
Hehe... Wasn't that amazing, Commander?
The most sublime element of its flavor... as I'm sure you're aware...
...Was the addition of our shared warmth.
